    OmicSelector_get_benchmark_methods

    Source: R/OmicSelector_get_benchmark_methods.R
    OmicSelector_get_benchmark_methods.Rd

    Get methods checked in benchmark.

    OmicSelector_get_benchmark_methods(
  benchmark_csv = "benchmark1578929876.21765.csv"
)

    Arguments

    benchmark_csv

    Path to benchmark csv file.

    Value

    Vector of feature selection methods checked.
